Robin Traywick Williams
The Key To The Quarter Pole
Robin Traywick Williams is the winner of the sixth Best Unpublished Novel contest sponsored by James River Writers and Richmond magazine. Her book, The Key to the Quarter Pole, centers on an independent woman with a passion for horse racing.
